snippet.title: Playne Gameplay : Evolve Mode
snippet.description:
Short gameplay footage of Evolve Mode that you unlock at end game. In Evolve, you can explore and meditate in a 25sqKm island.


Grow entire forests with your habit of meditation.

Playne Steam Store page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/86...
Website: https://www.playne.co
